---
<section class="manifesto" id="why">
  <div class="container manifesto__inner">
    <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Why ADVNTR Road Exists</p>
    <h2 class="manifesto__lead" data-reveal>
      The internet gives travelers more information than ever and less judgment than ever.
    </h2>
    <div class="manifesto__grid">
      <p class="manifesto__dropcap" data-reveal>
        Every trip-planning search now returns the same flattened pile: a hundred "top 10"
        lists, each one treating a shipwreck, a gas station, and the single most photographed
        formation on the coast as equally worth your afternoon. Generic lists don't help when
        every choice looks the same size.
      </p>
      <p data-reveal>
        ADVNTR Road tells you what matters, what to skip, where the tradeoffs actually are,
        and why — written with a literary voice and verified against official sources, not
        assembled from whichever posts ranked highest.
      </p>
      <p data-reveal>
        We write for road trippers, hotel-based travelers, campers, RVers, van travelers, and
        the fly-in-rental-car crowd alike. The format changes. The judgment doesn't.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto {
    background: var(--color-brunswick);
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    padding-block: var(--space-20);
  }
  .manifesto .eyebrow { color: var(--color-buff); }
  .manifesto__lead {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, var(--text-4xl));
    max-width: 20ch;
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
  }
  .manifesto__grid {
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }
  .manifesto__grid p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    color: var(--text-on-dark-secondary);
    max-width: var(--measure-prose);
  }
  .manifesto__dropcap::first-letter {
    float: left;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3.4em;
    line-height: 0.8;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-buff);
    padding-right: var(--space-2);
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .manifesto__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .manifesto__grid p { font-size: var(--text-base); }
  }
</style>
